    id: "RULE_ART_0533",
    subject: "Special dispensers",
    contextLocation: "Ontario",
    constraintType: "Prohibited",
    value: "Except as provided in Article 4.5.8.4. for card or key- activated equipment, special dispensers including coin-operated, card- operated and preset units, shall not be permitted at self-service outlets unless there is at least one qualified attendant on duty for each 12 hoses which can be operated simultaneously while the outlet is open to the public.",
