    id: "RULE_ART_0598",
    subject: "Explosion protection",
    contextLocation: "Ontario",
    constraintType: "Required",
    value: "(1) Processing equipment where an explosion hazard is present shall be (a) designed to withstand the explosion pressure without damage to the equipment, (b) provided with explosion venting in conformance with NFPA 68, \"Guide for Venting of Deflagrations\", or (c) provided with an explosion prevention system in conformance with NFPA 69, \"Standard on Explosion Prevention Systems\".",
