    value: "(1) Portable extinguishers shall be located so that they are easily seen and shall be accessible at all times, except as permitted in Sentences (2) and (3). (2) A lockable, break-front glazed cabinet may be used for security purposes to store portable extinguishers and where portable extinguishers are located in a fire hose cabinet, an approved lockable, scored glass break-front cabinet may be used. (3) In a detention occupancy, portable extinguishers are permitted to be located in secure areas, or in lockable cabinets provided (a) identical keys for all cabinets are located at all supervisory or security stations, or (b) electrical remote release devices that are designed to open upon power failure are provided for the cabinets.",
