    value: "Where smoke control measures contained in Commentary C of NRC, User's Guide -NBC 1995, \"Fire Protection, Occupant Safety and Accessibility (Part 3)\" are used, the inspections and tests shall be carried out as outlined in Section 7.3 in Division B of NRC, \"National Fire Code of Canada 2005\".",
